<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Welcome to Kyn</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-width: 100%;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      background-color: #FAFAFA;
      color: #222222;
    }

    a {
      color: #000;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    table td {
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #0070f3;
      padding: 24px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 24px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f6f6f6;
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0070f3;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>New Help Request 🚨</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Dear <%= firstName %>,</p>

      <p>
        A new help request has just been posted on <strong>Kyn</strong> that matches your interests.
      </p>

      <p>Here are the details:</p>

      <p><strong>Request Title:</strong> <%= requestTitle %></p>
      <p><strong>Kyn Reward:</strong> <%= KynReward %> Kyn</p>

      <% if (description) { %>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong></p>
        <p><%= description %></p>
      <% } %>

      <p>
        You can respond to this request if you're available to help. Your contribution will earn you the listed Kyn reward and help someone in the community.
      </p>

      <p><strong>Next steps:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Open the Kyn app or website.</li>
        <li>Go to the <strong>Help Requests</strong> section.</li>
        <li>Search for the request titled "<%= requestTitle %>".</li>
        <li>Click <strong>Respond</strong> to offer your help.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Thank you for being an active part of the Kyn community. Your kindness makes a real difference.
      </p>

      <p>Warm regards,<br/>— The Kyn Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>Need help? Contact us at 
        <a href="mailto:kyn.value@gmail.com">kyn.value@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>